{"word":"G4323 - προσανατίθημι - prosanatíthēmi - pros-an-at-ith'-ay-mee - In conference add","slug":"G4323","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προσανατίθημι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>prosanatíthēmi"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>pros-an-at-ith'-ay-mee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>In conference add"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x03C3;&#x03B1;&#x03BD;&#x03B1;&#x03C4;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03B8;&#x03B7;&#x03BC;&#x03B9; - prosanatithe&#x0304;mi</b> - <i>pros-an-at-ith'-ay-mee</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4314\">G4314</a> and <a href=\"#/G394\">G394</a>; to <i>lay up in addition</i>, that is, (middle voice and figuratively) to <i>impart</i> or (by implication) to <i>consult:</i> - in conference add, confer."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2652\">G2652</a>, <a href=\"#/G2653\">G2653</a>, <a href=\"#/G331\">G331</a>, <a href=\"#/G332\">G332</a>, <a href=\"#/G334\">G334</a>, <a href=\"#/G394\">G394</a>"}]}